OCaml Labs

These are software packages developed and maintained at OCaml Labs, either directly by us or with our industrial collaborators at Citrix, Jane Street, OCamlPro, and of course with a huge amount of help from the wider OCaml community.

ocaml-expect

  • version 0.0.2
  • 0.0.3
  • 0.0.4
Maintainer contact@ocamlpro.com
Dependencies ocamlfind & extlib = 1.5.3 & ounit & pcre-ocaml & oasis >= 0.3.0
Last update Dec 19, 2013
Source https://forge.ocamlcore.org/frs/download.php/475/ocaml-expect-0.0.2.tar.gz
723288a1c9078f86e6185e78a6baa577

Simple implementation of "expect" to help building unitary testing of interactive program

You can match the question using a regular expression or a timeout.

See the Expect manual for more information: http://expect.nist.gov/

Dependencies
oasis ( >= 0.3.0 )
pcre-ocaml
ounit
extlib ( = 1.5.3 )
ocamlfind
Required by
oasis
